Information
------------------------------
Model Neelam Gill takes us on a Private View of the Vogue 100: A Century of Style showcase at the National Portrait Gallery in London. The exhibition celebrates 100 years of cutting edge fashion, beauty and portrait photography by British Vogue. She shares her insights on the last century of British Vogue, including her own personal experiences, lifting the lid on one of the fashion world's greatest institutions.
